OL,6,FA biker who "made no significant
OL,7,Feffort to brake" chose "speed and
OL,8,Fexhilaration over safety" as he killed
OL,9,Fa pensioner as he crossed the road.
OL,11,FDaniel Rimmer, 22, failed to slow down
OL,12,Fin the dark "awful weather conditions"
OL,13,Fbefore ploughing into Clive Smees,
OL,14,Feven though police say he would have
OL,15,Fseen the pensioner ahead of him.
OL,17,FClive, 71, suffered catastrophic
OL,18,Finjuries and died on the scene, on
OL,19,FHaigh Road in the Aspull area of
OL,20,FWigan, at around 9.30pm on 18 May 2022.
