OL,6,FHis family say he is "dearly missed by
OL,7,Fhis loving wife, son and daughters and
OL,8,Fgrandchildren".
OL,10,FDetective Constable Phil Drummond,
OL,11,Ffrom Greater Manchester Police's
OL,12,FSerious Collision Investigation Unit,
OL,13,Fadded: "Rimmer knew the area; he knew
OL,14,Fthe time of evening and the likelihood
OL,15,Fof encountering pedestrians on his
OL,16,Fjourney. Despite the awful weather
OL,17,Fconditions, he chose speed and
OL,18,Fexhilaration over safety.
OL,20,F"His lack of responsibility resulted
OL,21,Fin Clive never returning home."
