OL,6,FRimmer pleaded guilty to causing death
OL,7,Fby dangerous driving, and was
OL,8,Fsentenced to three years and four
OL,9,Fmonths in prison at Bolton Crown Court.
OL,11,FHe has also ben banned from driving
OL,12,Ffor six years and eight months, and
OL,13,Fwill have to take an extended retest.
OL,15,FSpeaking after the sentencing, Clive's
OL,16,Ffamily said: "We have today sought
OL,17,Fjustice following Clive's untimely and
OL,18,Funnecessary death.
